data.description: #2805: Spacious Country Home! 4-6 bedroom/3 bath home on 30 acres m/l of excellent pasture land, fenced with a pond. Open concept kitchen & living room with vaulted ceiling. Granite custom cabinets, quality built in appliances, hardwoods, tile, carpet. Huge master suite with French doors leading to a large deck with hot tub 25+ acres of gently rolling hills. Many extras: two additional bedrooms downstairs, theater/game room, & tack room. White shed approximately 20x20 and a Red Barn approximately 20x30 pipe fencing down driveway and surrounding the yard. Pasture is perfect for horses or cattle.
